# CODEOWNERS - Code Review Ownership for HLD Documentation
# 
# This file defines ownership and review requirements for documentation changes.
# When a PR modifies files matching these patterns, the specified teams/users
# will be automatically requested as reviewers.
#
# Syntax: <file-pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Owners can be: @username @org/team-name

